# Project Overview

This is a Jira MCP (Model Control Protocol) connector that enables AI assistants like Claude to interact with Atlassian Jira. The project provides a seamless interface for AI models to perform common Jira operations through structured tool calls.

## Key Components

- **Entry Point**: [main.go](mdc:main.go) - Initializes and configures the MCP server with all Jira tools
- **Service Clients**: 
  - [services/jira.go](mdc:services/jira.go) - Jira client setup
  - [services/atlassian.go](mdc:services/atlassian.go) - Atlassian authentication and credentials